## Multiply `*` [esql-mul]

:::{image} ../../../images/operators/mul.svg
:alt: Embedded
:class: text-center
:::

Multiply two numbers together. If either field is [multivalued](/reference/query-languages/esql/esql-multivalued-fields.md) then the result is `null`.
